=== If Pressured by Physician

    - Cite NICE 2021 guidelines (UK), recent reviews documenting harm
    - Request pacing/energy envelope management instead
    - Seek second opinion from ME/CFS-knowledgeable physician
    - If insurance requires “exercise program,” document that standard GET worsens ME/CFS; request adaptive pacing therapy (APT) instead

